    <p>
      Salt Lake County gets hit by hail more often than most Utah homeowners expect. The valley's
      geography — sitting between the Wasatch Range to the east and the Oquirrh Mountains to the west —
      creates conditions that funnel summer storm cells directly over populated areas in Sandy, Draper,
